DTSTART:20260813T160000Z
DTEND:20260813T164500Z
SUMMARY:BayCare Presents Diabetes Trifecta- Awareness\, Eating\, and Every
 day Action
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Diabetes and prediabetes are more common than ever  but small 
 daily choices can make a big difference. This engaging session focuses on 
 under-standing personal risk\, simplifying healthy eating\, and incorporat
 ing realistic everyday actions that support better blood sugar control and
  overall health. Participants will leave with practical\, easy-to-apply st
 rategies to build healthier habits and take proactive steps toward prevent
 ion and wellness. August 13\, 2026 Martie Hale RDN 12- 12:45 pm Register H
 ere (https:events.teams.microsoft.comeventd0badb0c-f7eb-4316-941d-03bac319
 44d9599ceff3-02a8-45bc-baef-c48cb8be94c4) (Once you register the link will
